profile:
Total Painting has proudly been servicing Southern Georgian Bay for over 15 years.
Fine interior painting & spray finishing is our forte.
Within our team we have a broad skill set enabling us to go far beyond just painting. 
Recoating cabinetry, railings & furniture, replacing trim & building custom furniture pieces are some of our value added services.
Using only top quality finishing equipment & only using high line products are how we have gained our reputation. 
Total customer satisfaction is our only goal.
